	(text "25V -> 3V3 -> 2.5V\n\nG = 10k/(68k+10k)*3k/(1k+3k) = 0.09615\nVout@18V(Battery) = 1.731V\nVout@24V = 2.308V\nVout@PoE = 2.475\n\nfc = 1 / ( 2pi*68k*100n ) = 23Hz\nAccuracy: 1%-0.1% (depends on resistors' acc.)"
